== 政治 ==
[[File:Parliament_RM_front.jpg|left]]
{{main|摩尔多瓦政治}}
今天的摩爾多瓦是一個[[议会共和制|議會共和國]]。根據[[摩爾多瓦憲法_(1994年)|1994年頒佈的摩爾多瓦憲法]]，摩爾多瓦實行[[三權分立|三權分立]]，行政權屬於摩爾多瓦總理、立法權屬於[[摩爾多瓦議會|摩爾多瓦議會]]、司法權屬於摩爾多瓦[[憲法法院|憲法法院]]。[[摩爾多瓦議會|摩爾多瓦議會]]實行[[一院制|一院制]]，有101個議席，由4年一度的全國普選以[[比例代表制|比例代表制]]方式選出。摩爾多瓦的[[國家元首|國家元首]]是[[摩尔多瓦总统|摩爾多瓦總統]]，[[政府首腦|政府首腦]]是[[摩尔多瓦总理|摩爾多瓦總理]]，政府內閣由總理組建（唯內閣名單需要由議會批准）。摩爾多瓦曾一度規定總統由議會選出，但2016年開始又改爲[[全民普選|全民普選]]<ref name="const">{{cite web |url=http://www.e-democracy.md/en/legislation/constitution/ |title=The Constitution of the Republic of Moldova, 2000 |publisher=E-democracy.md |date= |accessdate=2013-10-09 |archive-date=2020-04-25 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200425182448/http://www.e-democracy.md/en/legislation/constitution/ |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref name=PRCE/><ref name=CIAM/><ref>{{cite news |url=http://jurnal.md/ro/justitie/2016/3/4/decis-seful-statului-va-fi-ales-de-popor-modificarea-din-2000-a-constitutiei-privind-alegerea-presedintelui-de-parlament-neconstitutionala/ |title=DECIS: Şeful statului va fi ales de popor; Modificarea din 2000 a Constituţiei privind alegerea preşedintelui de Parlament, NECONSTITUŢIONALĂ |newspaper=[[Jurnalul_Național|Jurnalul Național]] |date=2016-03-04 |language=ro |trans-title=DECIDED: The president will be elected by the people;  The 2000 amendment of the Constitution concerning the election of the President by Parliament unconstitutional |accessdate=2018-02-04 |archive-date=2021-02-25 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210225044414/https://www.jurnal.md/ro/justitie/2016/3/4/decis-seful-statului-va-fi-ales-de-popor-modificarea-din-2000-a-constitutiei-privind-alegerea-presedintelui-de-parlament-neconstitutionala/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

[[File:Chisinau_riot_2009-04-07_04.jpg|thumb]]中議會大樓前的抗議民眾]]
1994年的摩爾多瓦議會選舉中，{{link-en|摩爾多瓦農業黨|Agrarian Party of Moldova}}獲得多數選票，象徵着摩爾多瓦政治狀況的轉折<ref name=NS>[[Dieter_Nohlen|Nohlen, D]] & Stöver, P (2010) ''Elections in Europe: A data handbook'', p1330 {{ISBN|978-3-8329-5609-7}}</ref>{{rp|1342}}1996年，[[摩尔多瓦共和国共产党人党|摩爾多瓦共產黨人黨]]贏得總統選舉，代表該黨的[[彼得·盧欽斯基|彼得·盧欽斯基]]成爲摩爾多瓦第二任總統。2001年的議會選舉中，摩爾多瓦共產黨人黨再次大勝。摩爾多瓦第三任總統是同樣代表共產黨人黨的[[弗拉迪米尔·沃罗宁|弗拉迪米爾·沃羅寧]]<ref>{{Cite news|url=http://www.presedinte.md/eng/petru-lucinschi|title=Biography of President of the Republic of Moldova Petru Lucinschi, 1996-2001|access-date=2017-08-20|language=en|archive-date=2021-02-21|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210221123644/https://www.presedinte.md/eng/petru-lucinschi|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>"Moldovan communists determined to keep links with West", ''Kommersant'' (nl.newsbank.com), March 7, 2001.</ref>。摩爾多瓦共產黨人總體持親俄立場。該黨的衰落始於2009年該黨[[马里安·卢普|马里安·卢普]]轉投[[摩尔多瓦民主党|摩爾多瓦民主黨]]。她的轉投使不少共產黨人黨支持者轉而支持摩爾多瓦民主黨<ref>{{cite conference |first=Ion |last=Marandici |title=The Factors Leading to the Electoral Success, Consolidation and Decline of the Moldovan Communists' Party During the Transition Period |date=2010-04-23 |work=Midwestern Political Science Association Convention |publisher=Social Science Research Network |ssrn=1809029}}</ref>。2009年4月的議會選舉結果是摩爾多瓦共產黨人勝選，但這樣的結果不被社會大眾認可，由此引發了[[2009年摩爾多瓦抗議活動|大規模抗議活動]]<ref name="twitterrevolution">[http://www.spiegel.de/international/europe/0,1518,618563,00.html "Twitter Revolution: Fearing Uprising, Russia Backs Moldova's Communists"] {{Wayback|url=http://www.spiegel.de/international/europe/0,1518,618563,00.html |date=20110604155020 }}, Spiegel, April 10, 2009</ref><ref>[http://www.rferl.org/content/Moldovas_Twitter_Revolution/1605005.html "Moldova's "Twitter Revolution""] {{Wayback|url=http://www.rferl.org/content/Moldovas_Twitter_Revolution/1605005.html |date=20110629195218 }}, RFE/RL, April 8, 2009</ref>。7月，重新進行選舉。因無法就總統人選達成一致，2010年11月，摩爾多瓦議會再次進行議會選舉<ref name=rfe1>[http://www.rferl.org/content/Moldova_President_Dissolves_Parliament_Calls_Poll/1754890.html Moldova President Dissolves Parliament, Calls Poll] {{Wayback|url=http://www.rferl.org/content/Moldova_President_Dissolves_Parliament_Calls_Poll/1754890.html |date=20160303173144 }} [[Radio_Free_Europe/Radio_Liberty|Radio Free Europe/Radio Liberty]], 15 June 2009</ref><ref name=BBC1>[http://news.bbc.co.uk/2/hi/europe/8173649.stm Moldovans vote in election re-run] {{Wayback|url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/2/hi/europe/8173649.stm |date=20090730100943 }} [[BBC_News|BBC News]], 29 July 2009</ref>。2012年，獨立人士[[尼古拉·蒂莫夫蒂|尼古拉·蒂莫夫蒂]]出任總統<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.evz.ro/detalii/stiri/cine-e-nicolae-timofti-noul-presedinte-al-republicii-moldova-971858.html|title=Cine e Nicolae Timofti, noul președinte al Republicii Moldova?|language=ro|author=Paul Ciocoiu|date=2012-03-16|publisher=EVZ.ro|accessdate=2012-03-16|archive-date=2012-03-19|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120319020604/http://www.evz.ro/detalii/stiri/cine-e-nicolae-timofti-noul-presedinte-al-republicii-moldova-971858.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

2015-2016年，摩爾多瓦因經濟形勢惡化，國內出現{{link-en|2015-16年摩爾多瓦抗議活動|2015–16 protests in Moldova|大規模抗議}}。2016年開始，[[巴维尔·菲利普|巴维尔·菲利普]]出任摩爾多瓦總理，領導摩爾多瓦政府<ref name="theguardian.com_2016-02-16">{{cite news| url=https://www.theguardian.com/world/2016/jan/27/moldovan-prime-minister-pavel-filip-says-last-chance-to-end-national-crisis| title=Moldovan prime minister Pavel Filip says 'last chance' to end national crisis| newspaper=[[The_Guardian|The Guardian]]| date=2016-01-26| agency=[[Agence_France-Presse|Agence France-Presse]]| accessdate=2016-03-10| archive-date=2016-03-19| archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160319144817/http://www.theguardian.com/world/2016/jan/27/moldovan-prime-minister-pavel-filip-says-last-chance-to-end-national-crisis| dead-url=no}}</ref>。

今天，摩爾多瓦國內政壇仍然就採取親[[歐盟|歐盟]]還是親俄有着激烈分歧<ref>{{cite web|url=http://carnegieendowment.org/2017/05/23/moldova-between-russia-and-west-delicate-balance-pub-70056|title=Moldova Between Russia and the West: A Delicate Balance|author=EUGENE RUMER|publisher=carnegieendowment.org|access-date=2018-02-04|archive-date=2021-02-21|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210221123727/https://carnegieendowment.org/2017/05/23/moldova-between-russia-and-west-delicate-balance-pub-70056|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

